   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="uoedh_hl_h.1542_1.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address rend="letterhead">
                  <addrLine>RIVERSIDE COTTAGE</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>BEAMINSTER,</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>DORSET.</addrLine>
               </address>
               <dateline>
                  <date when="1925-02-04">February 4. 1925</date>
               </dateline>
               <salute>Dear Mr Hardy.</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I think I ought to tell you that I have written to <persName
                  ref="#ps:FrederickHarrison">Mr Harrison</persName> to tell him that I cannot play
                  "<persName ref="#ps:TessDurbeyfield">Tess</persName>" after all!</p>

            <p>I cannot part with <persName ref="#ps:DianaBugler">Diana</persName> and <persName
                  ref="#ps:ErnestBugler">my husband</persName> is not very happy about it all and I
               have no right to sacrifice <pb n="2" facs="uoedh_hl_h.1542_2.jpg"/>
               <pb n="3" facs="uoedh_hl_h.1542_3.jpg"/>
               <pb n="4" facs="uoedh_hl_h.1542_4.jpg"/> their happiness.</p>

            <p>I do not think <persName ref="#ps:FrederickHarrison">Mr Harrison</persName>
               <!-- check full name? -->will mind very much, for he probably knows that <persName
                  ref="#ps:SybilThorndike">Miss Thorndike</persName> is likely to produce the play
                  <damage agent="rust">later</damage> and that with her reputation the play <del>is
                     <unclear>more</unclear> likely to</del>
               <add place="above">will</add> be a greater success</p>

            <p>In a way, I am sorry, but I think it will be for the best.</p>

            <closer>
               <salute>Yours sincerely,</salute>
               <signed>Gertrude Bugler.</signed>
            </closer>
            <!-- duplicate link to p.2 below
               <pb n="2" facs="uoedh_hl_h.nnn.nn.nn_2.jpg"/>-->


